ic-nebudou-moci-kvuli-koronaviru-navstevy-neplati-pro-detska-oddeleni|title=V \u010cesku je 35 p\u0159\u00edpad\u016f n\u00e1kazy nov\u00fdm koronavirem. P\u0159ibyly na Zl\u00ednsku a v Praze|website=ct24.ceskatelevize.cz|access-date=9 March 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''34'''\n| 9 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}} \n| {{Partial failure|Person-to-person spread}}\n| {{flagicon|CZE}} known connection\n| [[Prague]]\n| [[Prague]]\n| {{Success|Home isolation}}\n| Male\n| ~12\n| {{flag|CZE}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | A young man (*2008) has family ties on a case infected in Italy. He was diagnosed at Bulovka Hospital in Prague.<ref name=\"case33-35.ct24\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''35'''\n| 9 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}} \n| {{Success|Travel-related}}\n| {{flag|Italy}}, [[Trentino]]\n| [[Prague]]\n| [[Prague]]\n| {{Success|Home isolation}}\n| Male\n| ~45\n| {{flag|CZE}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | A man (*1975) who returned from Lombardy, Italy. He was diagnosed at Bulovka Hospital in Prague.<ref name=\"case33-35.ct24\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''36'''\n| 9 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}} \n| {{Partial failure|Person-to-person spread}}\n| {{flagicon|CZE}} known connection\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{Success|Home isolation}}\n| Female\n| ~62\n| {{flag|CZE}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | A woman (*1958) with a connection to a group that was skiing in Val Gardena, Italy.<ref name=case36.twitter>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/adamvojtechano/status/1237046487453962242|title=Minister of Health announces case 36|via=Twitter |publisher=AdamVojtech|access-date=9 March 2020}}{{Primary source inline|date=April 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''37'''\n| 9 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}} \n| {{Success|Travel