elly |date=29 February 2020 |work=[[USA Today]] |url-status=live}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Mycfo\">{{cite web |url=https://www.who.int/news-room/detail/03-03-2020-shortage-of-personal-protective-equipment-endangering-health-workers-worldwide |title=Shortage of personal protective equipment endangering health workers worldwide |work=[[World Health Organization]] |access-date=5 March 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"S6DVx\">{{cite news |url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/02/27/investing/dow-stock-market-selloff/index.html |title=Dow falls 1,191 points \u2013 the most in history |last=Tappe |first=Anneken |publisher=[[CNN.com|CNN]] |access-date=28 February 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"U7teI\">{{cite news |last=Oh |first=Sunny |url=https://www.marketwatch.com/story/stocks-record-worst-week-since-financial-crisis-as-coronavirus-concerns-heat-up-2020-02-28 |title=Stocks record worst week since financial crisis as coronavirus concerns heat up |date=28 February 2020 |work=[[Market Watch]] |access-date=28 February 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"NRWqJ\">{{cite news |title=Scope affirms China's sovereign rating at A+ and maintains the Outlook at Negative |url=https://scoperatings.com/#!search/research/detail/162598EN |work=Scope Ratings GmbH |access-date=11 March 2020 |date=28 February 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"m0beI\">{{cite news |title=Stocks Plummet as Grim Economic Outlook Grips Markets: Live Updates |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/03/16/business/stock-market-today-coronavirus.html?action=click&module=Spotlight&pgtype=Homepage |work=[[The New York Times]] |access-date=16 March 2020 |date=16 March 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"5d3HR\">{{cite web |url=https://www.axios.com/coronavirus-recession-warnings-9eb743aa-2fd2-47ac-9e85-19ff54a07d3c.html |title=Economists now say the coronavirus could cause a recession |first=Dion |last=Rabouin |work=[[Axios (website)|Axios]] |date=28 February 2020 |access-date=16 March 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"swmUp\">{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/02/29/upshot/